OL,3,CTeens charged with arson attack which
OL,4,Cdestroyed former Debenhams store
OL,6,FDetectives investigating a fire at a
OL,7,Fformer Debenhams building in
OL,8,FCanterbury have charged two suspects.
OL,10,FNearby homes and businesses were
OL,11,Fevacuated and parts of the city centre
OL,12,Fwere cordoned off when the fire broke
OL,13,Fout at the former department store on
OL,14,FGuildhall Street on Monday 2 December
OL,15,F2024.
OL,17,FDrone images at the time captured the
OL,18,Fblackened building which was
OL,19,Fcompletely gutted by the fire.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/3
