OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1775229064
OL,3,CTeens charged with arson attack which
OL,4,Cdestroyed former Debenhams store
OL,6,FKent Police say initial enquiries were
OL,7,Fcompleted and arrests were made over
OL,8,Fthe next four days.
OL,10,FFollowing an investigation, two 17
OL,11,Fyear old boys appeared before
OL,12,FFolkestone Magistrates' Court on 17
OL,13,FMarch 2026 to each face a charge of
OL,14,Farson.
OL,16,FBoth were bailed with conditions to
OL,17,Fappear before the same court on
OL,18,FTuesday 14 April.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/3
